"1028","Item 61"
"1029","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"1030","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"1031","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum investment"
"1032","is waived if you make regular investments weekly, semimonthly, or"
"1033","monthly through automatic deductions through your bank checking"
"1034","or savings account. Currently, Putnam is waiving the minimum, but"
"1035","reserves the right to reject initial investments under the"
"1036","minimum."
"1037","Item 85B"
"1038","Additional Information About Errors and Omissions Policy"
"1039","While no claims with respect to the Registrant Series were filed"
"1040","under such policy during the period, requests under such policy"
"1041","for reimbursement of legal expenses and costs arising out of"
"1042","claims of market timing activity in the Putnam Funds have been"
"1043","submitted by the investment manager of the Registrant/Series."
